extends base-email

block content
  p Hello,
  p You've requested to reset your password. Click the button below to set a new password:
  div(style="text-align: center;")
    a.button(href=resetUrl) Reset Password
  p(style="color: #64748b; font-size: 0.875rem;")
    | Or copy and paste this link into your browser:
    br
    a(href=resetUrl, style="color: #3b82f6; word-break: break-all; font-size: 0.875rem;")
      | #{resetUrl}
  p If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.
